author: maxb
msg: * tools/dev/contribulyze.py (Contributor.canonical_name): Remove the fiction
about email-safe characters. Actually ensure that this function returns

author: lundblad
msg: Extend sussman's Big Lie
OR
Fix issue #2275: unfriendly error message when locking an already locked
file over ra_dav.
* subversion/mod_dav_svn/util.c
(dav_svn_convert_err): Translate the svn already locked error to 423 LOCKED.
* subversion/mod_dav_svn/lock.c
(dav_svn_get_locks, dav_svn_has_locks): Don't give a lock to the DAV
system if we're in a LOCK request, allowing the filesystem to
produce a better error.
